---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SEOHead from '../../components/SEOHead.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import FAQSchema from '../../components/FAQSchema.astro';
import TattooPriceCalculator from '../../components/TattooPriceCalculator.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <SEOHead slot="head" title="Tattoo Price Calculator — Free Pricing Estimator for Artists &amp; Clients" description="Estimate tattoo prices based on size, detail, placement, and artist experience. Free interactive calculator for artists and clients. No signup." />
  <FAQSchema data={{ questions: [
    { question: "Is the tattoo price calculator free?", answer: "Yes. Calculate unlimited estimates. No account or signup required." },
    { question: "What factors affect tattoo pricing?", answer: "Size, detail level, placement, color vs black and grey, artist experience, and studio location all impact the final price." },
    { question: "Can I use this for client estimates?", answer: "Yes. The calculator provides a starting point. Final pricing should be confirmed during consultation." },
    { question: "How accurate is the estimate?", answer: "Based on industry averages. Actual pricing varies by artist, studio, and geographic location." },
  ]}} />
  <Navbar />

  <section class="pt-24 pb-12 sm:pt-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-accent-400 mb-3">FREE TOOL</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white sm:text-5xl">Tattoo Price Calculator</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-400">Estimate tattoo prices based on size, detail, placement, and artist experience. A starting point for consultations and client quotes.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pb-12">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><TattooPriceCalculator /></div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16 bg-ink-900/20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center">Understanding Tattoo Pricing</h2>
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Size is the biggest price driver, but detail matters more than area.</h3><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">A small, highly detailed piece can cost more than a large, simple one. Fine line, dotwork, and color realism require more time and skill per square inch.</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Placement affects difficulty and therefore price.</h3><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Rib, spine, sternum, and hand/foot placements require more skill and accuracy. They're harder to heal and more painful — experienced artists charge more for these areas.</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Artist experience is priced into the rate.</h3><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Apprentice: $50-100/hr. Mid-level: $100-200/hr. Established: $200-350/hr. Celebrity/traveling: $350-500+/hr. Each level brings different speed and quality.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center">Pricing Guide by Tattoo Size</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-center text-gray-400">Average industry price ranges for common tattoo sizes (black and grey).</p>
      <div class="mt-8 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-ink-800">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead><tr class="border-b border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/50">
            <th class="px-5 py-3 text-left text-gray-300">Size</th>
            <th class="px-5 py-3 text-center text-gray-300">Estimated Range</th>
            <th class="px-5 py-3 text-center text-gray-300">Approx. Session Time</th>
            <th class="px-5 py-3 text-center text-gray-300">Best For</th>
          </tr></thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-ink-800">
            <tr><td class="px-5 py-3 text-white">Mini (1-2 inch)</td><td class="px-5 py-3 text-center text-gray-400">$50-150</td><td class="px-5 py-3 text-center text-gray-400">30-60 min</td><td class="px-5 py-3 text-center text-gray-400">Symbols, words, small flash</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-5 py-3 text-white">Small (3-4 inch)</td><td class="px-5 py-3 text-center text-gray-400">$150-300</td><td class="px-5 py-3 text-center text-gray-400">1-2 hrs</td><td class="px-5 py-3 text-center text-gray-400">Flowers, animals, script</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-5 py-3 text-white">Medium (5-7 inch)</td><td class="px-5 py-3 text-center text-gray-400">$300-600</td><td class="px-5 py-3 text-center text-gray-400">2-4 hrs</td><td class="px-5 py-3 text-center text-gray-400">Portraits, sleeves (partial)</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-5 py-3 text-white">Large (8-12 inch)</td><td class="px-5 py-3 text-center text-gray-400">$600-1500</td><td class="px-5 py-3 text-center text-gray-400">4-8 hrs</td><td class="px-5 py-3 text-center text-gray-400">Full sleeves, back pieces</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-5 py-3 text-white">Full Body / Sleeve</td><td class="px-5 py-3 text-center text-gray-400">$1500-5000+</td><td class="px-5 py-3 text-center text-gray-400">Multiple sessions</td><td class="px-5 py-3 text-center text-gray-400">Full sleeve, back, chest</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-gray-500 text-center">Color tattoos typically add 25-50% to the price. Custom designs add consultation time.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16 bg-ink-900/20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center">How to Set Your Studio's Pricing</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-center text-gray-400">Use these factors to determine your pricing strategy.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3 text-left">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-4"><h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Market Research</h3><p class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-400">Research local competitors. Check their pricing for similar size and style. Price competitively but don't undervalue your work.</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-4"><h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Cost + Margin</h3><p class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-400">Factor in supplies (ink, needles, gloves), studio rent, utilities, insurance, and your desired hourly rate. Set prices that cover costs plus 30-50% profit.</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-4"><h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Tiered by Artist</h3><p class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-400">Different rates for apprentice, junior, senior, and guest artists. InkFlow's commission system handles automatic split per artist rate.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Manage Pricing &amp; Bookings in One Place</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-gray-400">Set service prices, collect deposits at booking, and track revenue. InkFlow handles it all.</p>
    <a href="/features/tattoo-payment-processing" class="mt-6 inline-block rounded-lg bg-accent-500 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-ink-950 hover:bg-accent-400 transition-all">Learn More →</a>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600"><a href="https://app.ink-flows.com/register" class="text-accent-400 hover:underline">Try InkFlow Free →</a></p>
  </section>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
